               Hash Cond: (aqj_t1.a = aqj_t2.a)
               ->  Seq Scan on aqj_t1
               ->  Hash
                     ->  Seq Scan on aqj_t2
         ->  Hash
               ->  Seq Scan on aqj_t3
 Optimizer: Postgres query optimizer
(11 rows)

